{"id":404106,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/08/端传媒-学会这些-你也能编抗日神剧/","date":"2015-08-26T10:03:39Z","modified":"2015-08-26T10:03:39Z","title":"端传媒 | 学会这些 你也能编抗日神剧","content":"<p>采访了多位抗日神剧的新一代编剧们，我明白了剧本塑造的如下范式：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-404107\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751.png\" alt=\"cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/cd866575764a4711b663e8e1749b5751-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>【国民党军官】——弃暗投明、经受考验</p>\n<p>丧失斗志：对国军的腐化堕落绝望 /不满「攘外必先安内」消极抗日→</p>\n<p>挫败遭遇：抗日战场自己部队遭遇重创或官僚陷害→</p>\n<p>共军救星：重伤或被俘，八路军成救星→</p>\n<p>革命挫折：融入中共备受猜疑，但凭藉努力受到承认→</p>\n<p>久经考验：成为真正的「八路」将领</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-404108\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a.png\" alt=\"dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/dcab31fd86a14ce791d954a30d22166a-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>【平民百姓】——从 灭门血案中成长</p>\n<p>深仇大恨：全家/全村被日军屠戮→</p>\n<p>共军救星：杀鬼子身陷险境，受到中共/地方民兵的帮助/招募→</p>\n<p>革命挫折：「革命经验」不足，遭遇日军国民党特务/汉奸诱惑或欺骗→</p>\n<p>坚定信念：中共方面友人/爱人/家人遇害，坚定复仇之心→</p>\n<p>久经考验：经历抗战，成长为坚强的中共党员/革命战士</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-404109\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25.png\" alt=\"101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/101ebe74683d46cc98f1fba44ffe1a25-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>【江湖高手/商界奇才/知识份子】——以一当十、屡建奇功</p>\n<p>坚守中立：受到国共两党招募，但保持中立→</p>\n<p>挫折遭遇：日军拉拢/胁迫/侮辱， 奋起反抗遇挫败/打击日军阴谋，但终因寡不敌众被逼入绝路→</p>\n<p>共军救星：中共帮助脱险，受「革命精神」感召，作为周边人士参与革命→</p>\n<p>坚定信念：发现国民党抗日之不彻底，进一步信服於中共→</p>\n<p>以一当十：成为坚强的中共党员/革命战士</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-404110\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1.png\" alt=\"b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/b00b30683fb2402c9434364420a9b5e1-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>【八路军战士/中共党员】————革命勇士、魅力之神</p>\n<p>意志坚定：热血入党，「革命意志」坚定→</p>\n<p>忍辱卧底：隐身於民间，进入国民党/日军/土匪卧底→</p>\n<p>统一战线：一路上以强大的人格魅力/顽强革命精神收服前述的各方势力→</p>\n<p>以一敌百：壮大革命队伍，屡建奇功→</p>\n<p>革命功臣：迎来抗日胜利，革命故事在国共内战前戛然而止。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-404111\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d.png\" alt=\"51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d-70x70.png 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/08/51fa6e021e80405caf09c874aa99e92d-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>【日本鬼子】————战争狂人、冷血变态</p>\n<p>心怀不轨：试图一口吞下中国领土/人民财富。或甄别中方卧底/侦查受挫案件等</p>\n<p>步步紧逼：或杀或抢或骗，无所不用其极地强取豪夺，同时也收服了不少「汉奸」</p>\n<p>遭遇反抗：遭遇国民党军队/平民百姓/江湖高手/商界奇才/高智商知识份子的抵抗，损失惨重；但不思悔改</p>\n<p>共党出手：抗日力量在共产党的英明领导下，逐渐取得成绩；在节节败退中逐渐感到绝望</p>\n<p>引咎自裁：当然，不是切腹就是引弹自尽，场面需要血腥、酣畅</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534,13789],"tags":[9526,9040,9375,20434,12685,28400]}